Well, I had quite a long post written up, as I was in Florida last week and came back to having missed much of the thread.  Im not going to retype it, but I will touch on the highlights briefly.<br>
<br>
PoP boss mob loot is better than anything but some Ssra and most VT loot.  Guilds with no access to those mobs will find them quite rewarding, and even guilds with access will find these helpful to gear up with.<br>
<br>
As for Hunter/Forager Seb examples, those are instant spawns and thus have no basis for being on a rotation.  PoJ is a 30 min spawn, PoS named are a four hour spawn, all well below the standard rotation guidelines.  I would also point to the PoS Named in particular for being responsible for what has happened to the situation in BoT.<br>
